统雅伊尔·博尔索纳罗 (Jair Bolsonaro) 的电影进行了谈判获得财务支持&lt;/a&gt;，博尔索纳罗&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/z6e0Z9Z22-XlEPUsGESzUy-jrM9PAKaBWdteLXFW9sHxqiqba9jWZnF6NPKmuFTbbu-gyutZ3jVPHveOyclKCbVf6VdfdVw1pHWc5WqTvi7RSlDx7TXgBBrY8-8rrpL646l29cI8kY4J6xiKhbD5sqaWiQ0HKDAaekaPgtnkhP-HjCLIkBo6bXxJ3Ljh-a6gzf2cPySVvAKES9GBq7ix9NQ1pJmfoGhtwUuhkwDu75V0tnayZP4bseqvpU9OAwPh2dl8SrNeIqSblt_tHCXLvvTYpoENAPFff1y7rdnSBURqDhhFRhYfxhxOyS4y0qEXAakHyMnYT3gQUBk3LNy-RoZiXJgAOtUORX195c_qA04LRb_0mcYioriGnMY2mF6FBeuPTC9LXv69toVDZKfY_Xc2iC5BphIcB6D38na_xdjh1Dg7ZrYGvFPCF_zPziQ-8gReqBbeycLzn5QAoSIjZSFFKEe5hJLPdYiSOWKDioQ-qWDAF_Fisd7StyfNn8EpP3LHvRjCEb9it04_u3doE5EvE8NAcw/C8ZyUHmrLDPxWgTp2FV9q_U4x-6Dxx-Z/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="巴西最高法院暂停缩短博尔索纳罗刑期的法律"&gt;因企图右翼政变而被定罪&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;投资者担心该报告将削弱年轻的博尔索纳罗在十月选举中对总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦的挑战，从而推动了市场走势。 Banco Master SA 的大规模调查重新引发了选民对腐败的担忧，削弱了投票前对治理机构的信心。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/EsJDzFRl9PCFlkO2gLOigJCL359jD-QmttBFXIMPvAa9WjmzKHXIbZc2Cy1sOozbErpcO3z4N_di4V8BR11ItnPCEn4dVtJS-VbrWMvXzHeQNV5-CboELSr04GsvI-mGJLEs5lqLtIpjJK52KfCUvLc8vAIQFX2xVtNjNB085GCo4QM4MDkpuJBesf9cMCSAMr7JSC97Db7YylDFhbS-2DtWDTTYkvNEZsKHXLHwsLq28fgLc5C1n-mVy13u20NpwZu3IXHuoNsWQoUwl2S24FS0H1XcKYYswrjDXXgWhB0LpIPLWgHrhKia5fDy0HZIIHQ5DVuZOUJmh957q04Aq-b1jFp80MxB5FLux3IeJ_31s8bd9yQwQ6tRtremOHZMqw8pIxkIciROtsJeexD7qQ/SOJPQtTfAwtUWuNlrz_P2kvhYLdJ4Vqx/20" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 0 0 24px 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iqv_2DDqJzks/v0/-1x-1.jpg" alt="María Inés Barría Courtesy of Universidad San Sebastian" width